OL,3,C'Sadistic paedophile' Jon Ruben who
OL,4,Cinjected drugs into sweets is jailed
OL,6,FA summer camp leader who crushed up
OL,7,Fdrugs and injected them into sweets
OL,8,Ffor children has been jailed for 23
OL,9,Fyears and ten months.
OL,11,FFormer vet and church-goer Jon Ruben
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to 17 offences relating
OL,13,Fto incidents at the camp at Stathern
OL,14,FLodge in Leicestershire which he ran
OL,15,Ffor 27 years.
OL,17,FA number of children fell ill at the
OL,18,Fcamp near Melton Mowbray last year.
OL,19,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,20,Fthe day after receiving the report.
