OL,6,FRuben, of Wayte Court, Ruddington,
OL,7,FNottinghamshire, admitted sexual
OL,8,Fassault of a child under 13, assault
OL,9,Fof a child under 13 by penetration,
OL,10,Feight counts of child cruelty, three
OL,11,Fcounts of making indecent images of
OL,12,Fchildren and four drugs charges.
OL,14,FThe judge has sought to reassure the
OL,15,Fparents of boys sexually abused by Jon
OL,16,FRuben that they are not to blame for
OL,17,Fthe attacks, saying there is only "one
OL,18,Fperson to blame".
