OL,6,FJudge Timothy Spencer KC told
OL,7,FLeicester Crown Court: "As one mother
OL,8,Fhas accurately said, there's only one
OL,9,Fperson to blame for this, and that is
OL,10,FJon Ruben. That is the reality."
OL,12,FJudge Spencer said the impact of Jon
OL,13,FRuben's sexual abuse has "simply been
OL,14,Fdevastating".
OL,16,FThe judge told him: "The impact, Jon
OL,17,FRuben, that all of your offending has
OL,18,Fhad is palpable, and has been palpable
OL,19,Fin this court.
